erienced a spooky moment in 2008 where there was a ship coming towards me while I was swimming. I was freaking out because I\u0027d read articles about people losing their lives to ships because the ship crew didn\u0027t see the people swimming. And they ended up sailing right into the paths of the people swimming. The crew did see me though, which was a relief.","author":{"@type":"https://schema.org/Person","name":"@c.syde65","url":"https://www.youtube.com/@c.syde65","alternateName":"C. Syde65"},"upvoteCount":147}]}</script><script nonce="vMGQw-gK5pG0_1VTffrfpg">if (window.ytcsi) {window.ytcsi.tick('bc', null, '');}</script><link rel="preload" href="https://rr4---sn-h5576nsl.googlevideo.com/generate_204" as="fetch"><link rel="preload" href="https://rr4---sn-h5576nsl.googlevideo.com/generate_204" as="fetch" crossorigin><link rel="preload" href="https://rr2---sn-h557snzy.c.youtube.com/generate_204" as="fetch"><link rel="preload" href="https://rr2---sn-h557snzy.c.youtube.com/generate_204" as="fetch" crossorigin><link rel="canonical" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwHi916tJqY"><link rel="alternate" media="handheld" href="https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=qwHi916tJqY"><link rel="alternate" media="only screen and (max-width: 640px)" href="https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=qwHi916tJqY"><title>Spooky moment: Submarine passes beneath scuba divers - YouTube</title><meta name="title" content="Spooky moment: Submarine passes beneath scuba divers"><meta name="description" content="A submarine passed beneath some scuba divers in Waikiki, Hawaii on Friday. The divers were exploring the YO-257 shipwreck when the Atlantis submarine suddenl..."><meta name="keywords" content="CCTV, CGTN, CCTVNews, News, WorldNews, Submarine, Diver, ScubaDiver, Hawaii, Spooky, Diving"><link rel="shortlinkUrl" href="https://youtu.be/qwHi916tJqY"><link rel="alternate" href="android-app://com.google.android.youtube/http/www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwHi916tJqY"><link rel="alternate" href="ios-app://544007664/v